WEBVTT

00:00:00.240 --> 00:00:03.030
Hey, good morning everybody. How are

00:00:03.040 --> 00:00:05.349
y'all doing today? I'm Brandon

00:00:05.359 --> 00:00:07.510
Biggs and this is Diana Biggs, and we're

00:00:07.520 --> 00:00:09.589
excited to be with you all today. We

00:00:09.599 --> 00:00:10.870
have some things on our heart we're

00:00:10.880 --> 00:00:12.709
going to pray about. Remember

00:00:12.719 --> 00:00:14.870
the conference with Billy Brim?

00:00:14.880 --> 00:00:19.189
It's coming in February.

00:00:19.199 --> 00:00:21.429
Rick Renner and Billy Brim are going to

00:00:21.439 --> 00:00:24.070
do

00:00:24.080 --> 00:00:26.470
end times eschatology teachings.

00:00:27.840 --> 00:00:30.230
He is an expert

00:00:30.240 --> 00:00:33.350
in the Greek and she has been

00:00:33.360 --> 00:00:35.750
around for a long time learning about

00:00:35.760 --> 00:00:37.990
the end times. She's an expert in

00:00:38.000 --> 00:00:40.950
knowing the Bible

00:00:40.960 --> 00:00:43.750
and where we are with the end

00:00:43.750 --> 00:00:43.760
times—not

00:00:43.760 --> 00:00:45.190
being

00:00:45.190 --> 00:00:45.200
flaky,

00:00:45.200 --> 00:00:47.910
just straight-up Word of

00:00:47.920 --> 00:00:48.790
God,

00:00:48.800 --> 00:00:51.110
and I love that about them. I'm

00:00:51.120 --> 00:00:53.510
excited about it.

00:00:53.520 --> 00:00:55.910
It's a couple of months away,

00:00:55.910 --> 00:00:55.920
through

00:00:55.920 --> 00:00:57.430
November, December,

00:00:57.440 --> 00:00:59.510
and January, but it gives you enough

00:00:59.520 --> 00:01:01.029
time to pray about if you're supposed

00:01:01.039 --> 00:01:03.430
to be there. What a way to start the

00:01:03.440 --> 00:01:07.429
year off, getting yourself immersed in

00:01:07.439 --> 00:01:10.070
the Word of God and getting yourself ready

00:01:10.080 --> 00:01:12.149
for 2025.

00:01:12.159 --> 00:01:14.469
I believe we are going to see some major

00:01:14.479 --> 00:01:17.270
things in 2025, ladies and

00:01:17.270 --> 00:01:17.280
gentlemen—a

00:01:17.280 --> 00:01:20.230
great acceleration.

00:01:22.159 --> 00:01:24.390
Talking to

00:01:24.400 --> 00:01:27.350
you about that great acceleration, I

00:01:27.360 --> 00:01:31.830
warned you about New Orleans and I saw a

00:01:31.840 --> 00:01:34.310
one-man shooter,

00:01:34.320 --> 00:01:36.469
and that happened yesterday. My

00:01:36.479 --> 00:01:38.789
condolences to the families; we grieve

00:01:38.799 --> 00:01:41.429
with you. If you watch

00:01:41.439 --> 00:01:44.710
our YouTube channel, we pray

00:01:44.720 --> 00:01:47.429
for you. We know the loss of someone in

00:01:47.439 --> 00:01:50.789
your family is hard, and I pray

00:01:50.789 --> 00:01:50.799
for

00:01:50.799 --> 00:01:53.109
peace for your heart in

00:01:53.119 --> 00:01:56.469
this time of grieving.

00:01:56.479 --> 00:01:58.870
When I get a

00:01:58.880 --> 00:02:02.709
word from the Lord warning

00:02:02.719 --> 00:02:05.030
to pray for something, there are a lot

00:02:05.040 --> 00:02:06.870
of you that question if this guy is flaky or

00:02:06.880 --> 00:02:09.669
not. Now,

00:02:09.679 --> 00:02:11.190
I'm not trying to toot my own horn,

00:02:11.200 --> 00:02:13.750
folks, but I take it very

00:02:13.750 --> 00:02:13.760
seriously.

00:02:13.760 --> 00:02:16.470
I don't come on here just to waste my

00:02:16.480 --> 00:02:18.949
time; I come on here because the Lord

00:02:18.959 --> 00:02:21.670
has told me specifically, 'Brandon, I

00:02:21.680 --> 00:02:23.190
need you to sound the alarm and be a

00:02:23.200 --> 00:02:26.070
watchman for Me in these last

00:02:26.070 --> 00:02:26.080
days.'Whenever

00:02:26.080 --> 00:02:28.229
I come here and tell you

00:02:28.239 --> 00:02:30.470
there's an attack coming on New Orleans, we

00:02:30.480 --> 00:02:32.070
have to take it more seriously. It is

00:02:32.080 --> 00:02:35.030
a rebuke to me because I only prayed

00:02:35.040 --> 00:02:38.309
over it one time. We were

00:02:39.680 --> 00:02:41.509
interceding for it like we did

00:02:41.519 --> 00:02:43.030
for the presidency. When the Lord gives

00:02:43.040 --> 00:02:45.110
me an assignment, He

00:02:45.110 --> 00:02:45.120
showed me

00:02:45.120 --> 00:02:47.270
Nashville and

00:02:47.280 --> 00:02:49.430
Las Vegas. He

00:02:49.440 --> 00:02:51.110
said there are more cities,

00:02:51.120 --> 00:02:52.949
but He won't give those until

00:02:52.959 --> 00:02:54.630
later.

00:02:54.640 --> 00:02:57.430
The Lord

00:02:57.440 --> 00:02:59.670
showed me these three cities

00:02:59.680 --> 00:03:01.750
specifically;

00:03:01.760 --> 00:03:04.550
it wasn't Atlanta

00:03:04.550 --> 00:03:04.560
or

00:03:04.560 --> 00:03:08.630
New York. He said New Orleans,

00:03:08.640 --> 00:03:12.070
Nashville, and Las Vegas. The thing in

00:03:12.080 --> 00:03:14.630
Nashville happened—I think we

00:03:14.640 --> 00:03:16.309
averted it. It

00:03:18.080 --> 00:03:20.710
wasn't a shooting incident;

00:03:20.720 --> 00:03:25.110
it was a drone thing.

00:03:25.120 --> 00:03:26.710
I've been praying over these

00:03:26.720 --> 00:03:29.110
drones all the time, as they've been on my

00:03:29.120 --> 00:03:31.110
heart—strapping

00:03:31.120 --> 00:03:34.869
things to these devices and

00:03:34.879 --> 00:03:37.990
trying to cause mass destruction.

00:03:38.000 --> 00:03:40.070
The Lord already warned us; this is

00:03:40.080 --> 00:03:42.309
part of what I've been seeing. Well,

00:03:42.319 --> 00:03:45.190
that man was busted by the FBI. Glory to

00:03:45.200 --> 00:03:48.710
God! Then we have this man down

00:03:48.720 --> 00:03:50.470
there.

00:03:50.480 --> 00:03:52.869
When I was looking into the

00:03:52.879 --> 00:03:55.110
New Orleans thing, I saw that it was a

00:03:55.120 --> 00:03:58.949
one-person thing. Well,

00:03:58.959 --> 00:04:01.670
that happened; nine to eleven people were

00:04:01.680 --> 00:04:03.589
shot, and I think two people passed away,

00:04:03.599 --> 00:04:05.350
which is

00:04:05.360 --> 00:04:06.550
terrible.

00:04:06.560 --> 00:04:10.710
Now the next target

00:04:10.720 --> 00:04:12.789
I'm praying over is Las

00:04:12.799 --> 00:04:15.110
Vegas, specifically the Strip,

00:04:15.120 --> 00:04:17.430
praying that all

00:04:17.440 --> 00:04:19.189
the people there will

00:04:19.199 --> 00:04:21.830
not come into any harm's way. These

00:04:21.830 --> 00:04:21.840
are

00:04:21.840 --> 00:04:24.469
serious times, folks. When the Lord gives a word, it's

00:04:24.469 --> 00:04:24.479
not like we're just here to be entertained.

00:04:24.479 --> 00:04:28.070
I'm here to

00:04:28.080 --> 00:04:31.189
tell you what's coming, as the Lord

00:04:31.199 --> 00:04:33.270
has put me as a watchman on the wall,

00:04:33.280 --> 00:04:36.469
yelling out from a distance, 'Look,

00:04:36.479 --> 00:04:39.189
look, we must pray!'He said to raise up

00:04:39.199 --> 00:04:41.909
a million-person prayer army that

00:04:41.919 --> 00:04:43.430
will pray with you every

00:04:43.440 --> 00:04:45.430
single day.

00:04:45.440 --> 00:04:48.230
I believe we are on our

00:04:48.240 --> 00:04:51.350
way. We

00:04:51.360 --> 00:04:54.550
have about

00:04:54.550 --> 00:04:54.560
40,000

00:04:54.560 --> 00:04:57.030
people come and pray, and that's

00:04:57.040 --> 00:04:59.430
just the beginning. I believe this is

00:04:59.440 --> 00:05:01.350
going to grow and grow, and we

00:05:01.360 --> 00:05:03.270
are going to have

00:05:03.280 --> 00:05:05.749
results. People say,

00:05:05.759 --> 00:05:07.110
'Well, you called that out and we didn't

00:05:07.120 --> 00:05:08.950
see anything.'Praise God! That's

00:05:08.960 --> 00:05:11.510
what we want to happen. This is fruit

00:05:11.510 --> 00:05:11.520
from

00:05:11.520 --> 00:05:13.909
what the Lord is showing me,

00:05:13.919 --> 00:05:16.070
but

00:05:16.080 --> 00:05:19.510
we don't want to see our prayer

00:05:19.520 --> 00:05:21.110
fail;

00:05:21.120 --> 00:05:23.430
we want to see prayer success,

00:05:23.430 --> 00:05:23.440
which

00:05:23.440 --> 00:05:26.390
is peace and safety, and no weapon formed

00:05:26.400 --> 00:05:29.029
against these people

00:05:29.029 --> 00:05:29.039
prospering.

00:05:29.039 --> 00:05:31.990
Now we have a tragedy that happened, and

00:05:32.000 --> 00:05:33.590
it's terrible.

00:05:33.600 --> 00:05:35.590
Maybe we averted more;

00:05:36.880 --> 00:05:38.870
there could have been a

00:05:38.880 --> 00:05:40.950
bigger event or we could have delayed it.

00:05:47.680 --> 00:05:50.710
I don't want to see the wicked

00:05:50.720 --> 00:05:53.510
be successful in any plot or plan

00:05:53.520 --> 00:05:57.909
they have against people.

00:05:57.919 --> 00:05:59.670
We still don't have full election

00:05:59.680 --> 00:06:02.870
results; it's been going on for two weeks.

00:06:05.520 --> 00:06:07.430
They still haven't called the

00:06:07.440 --> 00:06:09.350
House completely.

00:06:12.240 --> 00:06:14.550
I told you corruption would

00:06:14.560 --> 00:06:17.029
be there and things would try to

00:06:17.039 --> 00:06:18.870
be delayed.

00:06:18.880 --> 00:06:20.629
Let's take communion

00:06:21.749 --> 00:06:21.759
and

00:06:24.000 --> 00:06:25.749
pray together,

00:06:25.749 --> 00:06:25.759
believing

00:06:25.759 --> 00:06:28.150
God that

00:06:28.160 --> 00:06:31.590
we have authority.

00:06:31.600 --> 00:06:34.469
We thank You,

00:06:34.479 --> 00:06:37.270
Father, that

00:06:37.280 --> 00:06:40.629
by Your stripes we are healed.

00:06:40.639 --> 00:06:42.950
You were wounded for our

00:06:42.960 --> 00:06:44.790
transgressions and bruised for our

00:06:44.800 --> 00:06:46.950
iniquities. The chastisement of our

00:06:46.960 --> 00:06:49.670
peace was upon You, and with Your

00:06:49.680 --> 00:06:53.029
stripes, we are healed

00:06:53.039 --> 00:06:54.950
physically, mentally, emotionally,

00:06:54.950 --> 00:06:54.960
and

00:06:54.960 --> 00:06:57.749
financially. We thank You for that Shalom, that peace

00:06:57.749 --> 00:06:57.759
that passes understanding. If Your Word abides in

00:06:57.759 --> 00:07:00.390
us,

00:07:05.270 --> 00:07:05.280
we

00:07:11.360 --> 00:07:13.430
shall ask what

00:07:13.430 --> 00:07:13.440
we

00:07:13.440 --> 00:07:16.309
will and it shall be done.

00:07:20.960 --> 00:07:22.710
We stand on the Word of God

00:07:22.720 --> 00:07:25.830
today and

00:07:25.840 --> 00:07:28.150
believe we receive

00:07:28.160 --> 00:07:30.870
deliverance in the name of Jesus over

00:07:30.880 --> 00:07:33.670
our bodies.

00:07:44.880 --> 00:07:46.950
We apply

00:07:49.120 --> 00:07:52.070
the blood of Jesus over

00:07:52.080 --> 00:07:55.110
Diana,

00:07:55.120 --> 00:07:56.950
from

00:07:56.960 --> 00:07:58.309
the top of her head to the soles of her

00:07:58.319 --> 00:07:59.990
feet, and over my

00:08:00.000 --> 00:08:02.629
children,

00:08:02.639 --> 00:08:05.189
our finances, our

00:08:05.199 --> 00:08:07.909
house, our car, and our

00:08:07.919 --> 00:08:09.909
jobs. According to Deuteronomy 28, we are blessed in the city and in the field, coming in and going out. Thank You, Lord, that we walk in divine health and have supernatural wisdom. I thank You for creative ideas to get wealth and that everything we put our

00:08:09.919 --> 00:08:14.309
hands to would prosper.

00:08:55.519 --> 00:08:58.150
We take authority over

00:08:58.160 --> 00:09:02.630
any kind of confusion.

00:09:02.630 --> 00:09:02.640
As

00:09:02.640 --> 00:09:04.550
it

00:09:04.550 --> 00:09:04.560
says

00:09:04.560 --> 00:09:06.389
in 2 Timothy

00:09:06.399 --> 00:09:09.110
1:7, God has not given us a spirit of

00:09:09.120 --> 00:09:12.550
fear but of power, and of love, and of

00:09:12.560 --> 00:09:15.829
a well-balanced mind. I thank You

00:09:21.269 --> 00:09:21.279
for

00:09:27.279 --> 00:09:29.509
mental clarity

00:09:29.509 --> 00:09:29.519
and

00:09:29.519 --> 00:09:32.150
focus so

00:09:32.150 --> 00:09:32.160
that

00:09:32.160 --> 00:09:34.310
we hear You

00:09:34.310 --> 00:09:34.320
and

00:09:34.320 --> 00:09:37.030
will not follow

00:09:37.030 --> 00:09:37.040
a

00:09:37.040 --> 00:09:39.350
stranger's

00:09:39.350 --> 00:09:39.360
voice.

00:09:39.360 --> 00:09:42.310
There

00:09:42.310 --> 00:09:42.320
are

00:09:42.320 --> 00:09:44.630
a

00:09:44.630 --> 00:09:44.640
lot

00:09:44.640 --> 00:09:46.550
of

00:09:46.550 --> 00:09:46.560
people

00:09:46.560 --> 00:09:57.750
here

00:10:06.550 --> 00:10:06.560
from

00:10:11.190 --> 00:10:11.200
different

00:10:16.000 --> 00:10:17.269
backgrounds—Catholic,

00:10:20.560 --> 00:10:23.590
Methodist,

00:10:23.600 --> 00:10:25.269
LDS—from

00:10:25.279 --> 00:10:27.190
all over the world.

00:10:28.959 --> 00:10:31.670
You may not always agree

00:10:31.680 --> 00:10:33.750
with how I take communion,

00:10:58.079 --> 00:11:00.389
but my

00:11:00.399 --> 00:11:02.870
heart is right and we love the Lord.

00:11:02.870 --> 00:11:02.880
It's all about having a relationship

00:11:02.880 --> 00:11:05.590
with the Lord Jesus Christ. Those who seek Him

00:11:05.590 --> 00:11:05.600
will

00:11:05.600 --> 00:11:07.590
find Him,

00:11:09.360 --> 00:11:11.670
and that's what we're all trying to

00:11:11.680 --> 00:11:14.069
do on this channel.

00:11:53.440 --> 00:11:57.030
Our number one goal is just

00:11:57.040 --> 00:11:59.590
to smile at Jesus today.

00:11:59.600 --> 00:12:00.630
It's

00:12:06.639 --> 00:12:09.350
not about race,

00:12:09.360 --> 00:12:11.269
gender,

00:12:11.269 --> 00:12:11.279
or

00:12:11.279 --> 00:12:14.069
money;

00:12:18.399 --> 00:12:21.509
we look at Jesus.

00:12:27.600 --> 00:12:29.990
I'm

00:12:34.320 --> 00:12:36.870
excited that we break down those

00:12:36.880 --> 00:12:40.069
walls; we're just

00:12:40.720 --> 00:12:43.190
one big happy family

00:12:43.200 --> 00:12:43.750
in

00:12:46.230 --> 00:12:46.240
the

00:12:48.560 --> 00:12:51.350
body

00:12:52.959 --> 00:12:53.430
of

00:12:58.629 --> 00:12:58.639
Christ.

00:13:04.959 --> 00:13:07.110
We can

00:13:07.120 --> 00:13:09.750
have doctrinal differences,

00:13:09.760 --> 00:13:12.629
but we can agree

00:13:12.639 --> 00:13:14.710
to disagree

00:13:14.720 --> 00:13:16.230
and love

00:13:16.240 --> 00:13:17.509
each other. It's like a family

00:13:19.600 --> 00:13:20.870
reunion—you

00:13:23.920 --> 00:13:25.509
might

00:13:28.000 --> 00:13:29.590
not

00:13:31.839 --> 00:13:33.990
agree with

00:13:34.000 --> 00:13:37.190
everything, but you still give them a hug. Politics

00:13:37.190 --> 00:13:37.200
is

00:13:37.200 --> 00:13:38.870
a big one,

00:13:43.200 --> 00:13:44.710
but we

00:13:44.710 --> 00:13:44.720
are

00:13:44.720 --> 00:13:46.470
family

00:13:53.040 --> 00:13:57.030
and

00:14:03.600 --> 00:14:05.670
we still

00:14:05.680 --> 00:14:08.870
love each other.

00:14:13.920 --> 00:14:16.310
I felt

00:14:16.320 --> 00:14:18.069
in my spirit

00:14:19.509 --> 00:14:19.519
that

00:14:23.120 --> 00:14:23.829
the Holy Spirit said

00:14:23.839 --> 00:14:26.550
to

00:14:26.560 --> 00:14:28.790
address

00:14:28.800 --> 00:14:30.230
that.

00:14:30.240 --> 00:14:32.470
Father,

00:14:43.040 --> 00:14:45.670
we take authority over any kind of

00:14:45.680 --> 00:14:50.150
demonic attack over Nevada and Las Vegas.

00:14:50.150 --> 00:14:50.160
We

00:14:50.160 --> 00:14:52.949
pray

00:14:52.949 --> 00:14:52.959
that

00:14:52.959 --> 00:14:56.069
all hidden

00:14:56.079 --> 00:14:58.790
things be revealed and that there will be no plots,

00:14:58.790 --> 00:14:58.800
calamities,

00:14:58.800 --> 00:15:02.790
shootings,

00:15:02.790 --> 00:15:02.800
or

00:15:02.800 --> 00:15:05.910
bombings in any hotel or

00:15:05.920 --> 00:15:09.430
casino. I plead the blood of

00:15:09.440 --> 00:15:12.470
Jesus over the Strip.

00:15:14.560 --> 00:15:17.030
Where sin abounds, grace does

00:15:17.040 --> 00:15:19.189
much more abound.

00:15:19.199 --> 00:15:22.790
We call forth all these things to be

00:15:22.790 --> 00:15:22.800
revealed—anything

00:15:22.800 --> 00:15:26.949
the devil has tried

00:15:26.959 --> 00:15:30.150
to stir up.

00:15:41.680 --> 00:15:43.910
We wrestle not

00:15:43.920 --> 00:15:46.949
against flesh and blood, but

00:15:46.959 --> 00:15:49.350
against principalities

00:15:49.360 --> 00:15:51.030
and powers.

00:16:11.120 --> 00:16:12.710
I just saw in a

00:16:12.720 --> 00:16:15.430
vision to pray over

00:16:22.000 --> 00:16:24.069
the Macy's Thanksgiving Day Parade. I pray a hedge of protection around those people in New York and call for an uncovering of darkness. I thank

00:16:24.069 --> 00:16:24.079
You that the NYPD, FBI, and CIA would have supernatural thinking to check things they might not otherwise check. I pray for

00:16:24.079 --> 00:16:26.710
a covering

00:16:26.720 --> 00:16:29.269
over

00:17:07.039 --> 00:17:08.710
families

00:17:38.400 --> 00:17:40.070
during the Christmas season

00:17:49.520 --> 00:17:53.029
and

00:18:03.200 --> 00:18:04.950
over the

00:18:04.960 --> 00:18:06.710
shopping malls.

00:18:49.360 --> 00:18:52.150
I pray for a

00:18:52.160 --> 00:19:02.150
special hedge of protection

00:19:09.200 --> 00:19:14.870
over Atlanta, Georgia.

00:19:22.480 --> 00:19:24.470
As people travel

00:19:30.799 --> 00:19:33.750
on American, United,

00:19:33.760 --> 00:19:36.390
Southwest, and other flights,

00:19:36.400 --> 00:19:38.470
I call

00:19:38.470 --> 00:19:38.480
for

00:19:38.480 --> 00:19:42.710
protection

00:19:42.710 --> 00:19:42.720
during

00:19:42.720 --> 00:19:44.789
this

00:19:44.799 --> 00:19:47.110
busiest traveling time.

00:19:47.110 --> 00:19:47.120
We

00:19:47.120 --> 00:19:49.750
